Sam’s is a tiny local downtown diner that puts together an amazing breakfast for cheap.   It was the first breakfast place we tried in C-U & still our favorite place for a casual Sunday morning.  The hash browns are perfectly crispy & light brown.   Sam’s French Toast is the thing!   They have half-orders so you can have both without wrecking the diet.  Wait staff is friendly & knows their regulars.  There are lots of regulars.  Lunchtime sandwiches are all diner style & taste great.  Not greasy, like some small diners.
